"{\n  \"text\": \"Hi everybody, Scotty here with Scotty's Fermented Foods. Ever wonder why vitamins sometimes work, sometimes don't? You ever talk to someone an emick who takes iron pills? Doesn't do anything? It's because the vitamins that you're taking are just the chemistry side of your nutrient absorption, and that's not the way your body works. Your body absorbs nutrients through the microbiome, and then the microbiome distributes it to the body as it's needed and just the quantities it's needed. And so if you don't have your microbiome working on all cylinders, a lot of times just taking the chemical nutrients isn't going to solve the problems. That's why you eat fermented foods. Like my garlic sauerkraut. Excellent living foods, full of the biology, the microbiome-added supplements that your body needs. Don't forget the microbiome. That's so important for nutrient absorption. Anyway, Scotty'sFoods.com is where you can get it all. Four atoms is free shipping. Thanks a lot, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hi everybody, Scotty here with Scotty's Fermented Foods.\",\n      \"start\": 0.24,\n      \"end\": 2.88,\n      \"duration\": 2.64,\n      \"confidence\": 0.991,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" Hi\",\n          \"start\": 0.24,\n          \"end\": 0.4,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 0.998\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 0.48,\n          \"end\": 0.56,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 0.56,\n          \"end\": 0.64,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"ody\",\n          \"start\": 0.64,\n          \"end\": 0.8,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \",\",\n          \"start\": 0.8,\n          \"end\": 0.